trans-unit.source: Represents the <xref uid="langword_csharp_maxInclusive" name="maxInclusive" href=""></xref> element from XML Schema as specified by the World Wide Web Consortium (W3C).
trans-unit.target: Representerar den <xref uid="langword_csharp_maxInclusive" name="maxInclusive" href=""> </xref> element från XML-Schema som anges av World Wide Web Consortium (W3C).

trans-unit.source: This class can be used to specify a restriction on the maximum value of a <xref uid="langword_csharp_simpleType" name="simpleType" href=""></xref> element.
trans-unit.target: Den här klassen kan användas för att ange en begränsning på det maximala värdet för en <xref uid="langword_csharp_simpleType" name="simpleType" href=""> </xref> element.

trans-unit.source: The element value must be less than or equal to the value of the <xref uid="langword_csharp_maxInclusive" name="maxInclusive" href=""></xref> element.
trans-unit.target: Elementvärdet måste vara mindre än eller lika med värdet för den <xref uid="langword_csharp_maxInclusive" name="maxInclusive" href=""> </xref> element.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaMaxInclusiveFacet"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaMaxInclusiveFacet"> </xref> klass.
